I just posted a negative one I have never posted in public in our Eastern Paranormal folder. By negative, I mean how they describe 2012 verses current New Age Thought. I posted the one titeled : 2012 Q&A? Answer Fire.....Skulls Melt

These sort of replies are what my husband calls my &quot;Night Light Ghost Boxing,&quot; because when I lay and think about them, then I get up and turn on my night light. 

We will keep on asking the 2012 questions as part of our 2012 series, but honestly if nothing else it makes you think a lot about your own life and what happens when we pass. I am much more aware of my actions now, and make sure that I always treat others and I would like to be treated.  

